org.fcrepo.kernel.impl.rdf.impl

Class DefaultIdentifierTranslator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fcrepo.kernel.impl.rdf.impl.DefaultIdentifierTranslator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IdentifierTranslator

    public class DefaultIdentifierTranslator
extends Object
implements IdentifierTranslator
    A very simple IdentifierTranslator which translates JCR paths into un-dereference-able Fedora subjects (by replacing JCR-specific names with Fedora names). Should not be used except in "embedded" deployments in which no publication of translated identifiers is expected!
    Since:
    May 15, 2013
    Author:
    barmintor, ajs6f
